text: Jenny Schumacher (10 September 1921 - November 2003) was a Belgian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Belgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Liège
